OL,3,CProgramme listings for
OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 13 APR
OL,4,G1400FWonderland: From JM Barrie to JRR
OL,5,     FTolkien
OL,6,     GIn a four-part series, immerse
OL,7,     Gyourself in the worlds of some of
OL,8,     Ghistory's finest authors,
OL,9,     Grevealing much about their
OL,10,     Gcharacter and the time they lived
OL,11,     Gin.
OL,12,G1500FStories From The National
OL,13,     FPortrait Gallery
OL,14,     GKate Bryan explores 20th-century
OL,15,     Gportraiture, examining depictions
OL,16,     Gof war poets and Queen Elizabeth
OL,17,     GII. Jim Moir drops in to discuss
OL,18,     Ghis favourite work.
