OL,7,     Gtheir audience in Cortona with a
OL,8,     Gmagical and starlit performance
OL,9,     Gthat includes Rota's Love Theme
OL,10,     Gfrom The Godfather.
OL,11,G2150FMozart's Women: A Musical Journey
