OL,4,G0430FAuction: Lord Lucan Special
OL,5,     GAristocrat Lord Lucan
OL,6,     Gmysteriously disappeared in 1974
OL,7,     Gafter being accused of murdering
OL,8,     Ghis children's nanny. Now, items
OL,9,     Gfrom the family home have come up
OL,10,     Gfor sale at Bonhams.
OL,11,G0500FAuction
OL,12,     GIt could be the most expensive
OL,13,     Gsale in the history books as the
OL,14,     Gextraordinary art collection of
OL,15,     GDavid and Peggy Rockefeller comes
OL,16,     Gto Christie's in New York.
